[
  "Former pharma salesman B.R. Shetty immigrated from Karnataka in south India to Abu Dhabi in 1973 to set up a healthcare empire.",
  "His biggest asset is London-listed NMC Health, one of the UAE's largest hospital chains.",
  "In May 2019, Shetty listed Finabir, the holding firm for his money remittance firms UAE Exchange and Travelex Group. ",
  "Shetty also owns healthcare firm BR Life, which has a presence in India, Nepal, Africa and the Gulf region.",
  "Shetty's son Binay is chief executive of BRS Ventures, the family's holding company."
]